<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-style>.mjbody a, .mjbody a:hover, .mjbody a:active, .mjbody a[href], .mjbody a[href]:hover, .mjbody a[href]:active {color: inherit;text-decoration: underline}</mj-style>
    <mj-breakpoint width="480px" />
  </mj-head>
  <mj-body width="600px" background-color="#E8EEFC" css-class="mjbody">
    <mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-bottom="0px" background-color="#66ABEE"><mj-column>

        <mj-image align="left" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="20px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="20px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/5tcczr6n_1773339200767_EM1_B2C_Mar17_Desktop_600px_2x_01KKHM1JVZC0F814KKDJY4C8VB.png" alt="Gamma Imagine. Create any graphic." width="600px" href="https://email.gamma.app/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnU09qd2NEQUlITXR4bUF6TGNaQVowQ25rUlk0QmhybEFZcVgwWlB3UT09IiwiaHJlZiI6Imh0dHBzOi8vZ2FtbWEuYXBwL2NyZWF0ZS9nZW5lcmF0ZSIsImludGVybmFsIjoiOGU4ZjA3ZjEwZGQwZTcwMTgxY2NiNzE5IiwibGlua19pZCI6MTk2OX0/de376224f74e9c091ffb988b913ea3df162e8147183cc24f29cfa5e1b1862569"></mj-image>

      </mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-right="20px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="20px" background-color="#66ABEE"><mj-column background-color="#FEFEFE" border-radius="18px">

        <mj-text color="#000E21" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.5" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="40px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="40px">Smiles, we're launching three major updates that work together to keep your best work in one place:</mj-text>

        <mj-text color="#000E21" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="44px" line-height="1.1" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="20px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="40px" font-weight="700">Gamma Imagine</mj-text>

        <mj-text color="#000E21" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.5" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="20px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="20px" padding-left="40px">Describe an idea — however vague — and&nbsp;<strong>Gamma Imagine</strong> explores different creative angles for you. Pick the direction that feels right, and Imagine produces polished, on-brand options in seconds. Logos, infographics, diagrams, social visuals, and more.</mj-text>

        <mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="40px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/6o5qy46b_1773426330103_Feature_GammaImagine_480px_2x_01KKM74J6EHD7DM6SHVJM9KJG3.png" alt="Pick a starting concept" width="480px" href="https://email.gamma.app/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnU09qd2NEQUlITXR4bUF6TGNaQVowQ25rUlk0QmhybEFZcVgwWlB3UT09IiwiaHJlZiI6Imh0dHBzOi8vZ2FtbWEuYXBwL2NyZWF0ZS9nZW5lcmF0ZSIsImludGVybmFsIjoiOGU4ZjA3ZjEwZGQwZTcwMTgxY2NiNzE5IiwibGlua19pZCI6MTk2OX0/de376224f74e9c091ffb988b913ea3df162e8147183cc24f29cfa5e1b1862569"></mj-image>

        <mj-text color="#000E21" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.5" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="20px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="40px">For the next 30 days,&nbsp;<strong>Gamma Imagine</strong> is available across all plans with expanded usage.&nbsp;<a href="https://email.gamma.app/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnU09qd2NEQUlITXR4bUF6TGNaQVowQ25rUlk0QmhybEFZcVgwWlB3UT09IiwiaHJlZiI6Imh0dHBzOi8vZ2FtbWEuYXBwL2NyZWF0ZS9nZW5lcmF0ZSIsImludGVybmFsIjoiOGU4ZjA3ZjEwZGQwZTcwMTgxY2NiNzE5IiwibGlua19pZCI6MTk2OX0/de376224f74e9c091ffb988b913ea3df162e8147183cc24f29cfa5e1b1862569" style="color: #1862D4; text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Try it now</strong></a> and see what you come up with.</mj-text>

        <mj-text color="#000E21" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="44px" line-height="1.1" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="20px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="40px" font-weight="700">Connectors</mj-text>

        <mj-text color="#000E21" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.5" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="20px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="20px" padding-left="40px">Gamma is everywhere you work. With a new suite of connectors, Gamma is now inside the tools you use every day: Claude, ChatGPT, and dozens more.</mj-text>

        <mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="40px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/uzzj9f6p_1773426331510_Feature_Integrations_480px_2x_01KKM74KHMX7SMYH9JF0V2H86X.png" alt="Gamma Connectors" width="480px" href="https://email.gamma.app/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnU09qd2NEQUlITXR4bUF6TGNaQVowQ25rUlk0QmhybEFZcVgwWlB3UT09IiwiaHJlZiI6Imh0dHBzOi8vZ2FtbWEuYXBwL2ludGVncmF0aW9ucyIsImludGVybmFsIjoiOGU4ZjA3ZjEwZGQwZTcwMTgxY2NiNzE5IiwibGlua19pZCI6MTk2OH0/19e3bc327c4c18195c3564e19fca760bb392d6c71e72284be5360baba72ee8fd"></mj-image>

        <mj-text color="#000E21" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.5" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="20px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="40px">Turn a conversation with Claude into a presentation. Turn an email into a deck for a prospect. The context is already there. Gamma turns it into something you can present, without switching tabs.</mj-text>

        <mj-text color="#000E21" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="44px" line-height="1.1" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="20px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="20px" padding-left="40px" font-weight="700">AI-native Templates</mj-text>

        <mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="40px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/0wcdtgj0_1773426333201_Feature_Templates_Blue_480px_2x_01KKM74N6HT7TKA9G14SPFFBM2.png" alt="Generate from template" width="480px" href="https://email.gamma.app/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnU09qd2NEQUlITXR4bUF6TGNaQVowQ25rUlk0QmhybEFZcVgwWlB3UT09IiwiaHJlZiI6Imh0dHBzOi8vZ2FtbWEuYXBwL3RlbXBsYXRlcyIsImludGVybmFsIjoiOGU4ZjA3ZjEwZGQwZTcwMTgxY2NiNzE5IiwibGlua19pZCI6ODR9/0c7c128f2aa0e8c3db5b97c6f9af1f3117d2159208bdfe78e8b4c1aac58da968"></mj-image>

        <mj-text color="#000E21" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.5" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="20px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="40px">We've completely rebuilt the template experience. Pick any template, tell Gamma what you need, and get a complete, polished deck in seconds. Change the content, the topic, the look. Gamma rebuilds the rest, with your brand intact every time.</mj-text>

        <mj-text color="#000E21" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.5" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="20px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="20px" padding-left="40px"><a href="https://email.gamma.app/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnU09qd2NEQUlITXR4bUF6TGNaQVowQ25rUlk0QmhybEFZcVgwWlB3UT09IiwiaHJlZiI6Imh0dHBzOi8vZ2FtbWEuYXBwL3RlbXBsYXRlcyIsImludGVybmFsIjoiOGU4ZjA3ZjEwZGQwZTcwMTgxY2NiNzE5IiwibGlua19pZCI6ODR9/0c7c128f2aa0e8c3db5b97c6f9af1f3117d2159208bdfe78e8b4c1aac58da968" style="color: #1862D4; text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Get started with 100+ new</strong></a>, professionally designed templates.</mj-text>

        <mj-button background-color="#1862D4" border-radius="50px" color="#FEFEFE" font-family="Helvetica, sans-serif" font-size="18px" font-weight="400" line-height="1.5" inner-padding="12px 30px 12px 30px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="40px" href="https://email.gamma.app/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnU09qd2NEQUlITXR4bUF6TGNaQVowQ25rUlk0QmhybEFZcVgwWlB3UT09IiwiaHJlZiI6Imh0dHBzOi8vZ2FtbWEuYXBwLyIsImludGVybmFsIjoiOGU4ZjA3ZjEwZGQwZTcwMTgxY2NiNzE5IiwibGlua19pZCI6NX0/b2affcfd3d0caa17592b9e49d58ac5725631270efa59f0cb3b66fe7a00040d08">Create Something Today&nbsp;<img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/lq02cyd5_1765815612476_icon_stars_26px_1x_01KCHCZXCEWKFY8GNJ4GJ0YWKF.png" alt="star icon" height="20" style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:middle;" /></mj-button>

        <mj-text color="#000E21" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.5" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="20px" padding-right="40px" padding-bottom="40px" padding-left="40px">Best,<br />Grant<br />Co-founder & CEO, Gamma</mj-text>

      </mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" background-color="#343680"><mj-column>

